<i>noun</i>: 배회 [배회/배훼], 방황 [방황], 방랑 [방ː낭] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>배회 [배회/배훼]</dt><br>
<dd>loitering; roaming</dd><br>
<dd>특별한 목적이 없이 어떤 곳을 중심으로 이리저리 돌아다님.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of wandering around a certain place without any definite purpose.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>방황 [방황]</dt><br>
<dd>1. wandering; roaming</dd><br>
<dd>이리저리 헤매며 돌아다님.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of wandering from place to place.</dd><br>
<dd>2. wandering</dd><br>
<dd>목표나 방향을 정하지 못하여 어찌할 바를 모르고 헤맴.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of wandering around, not knowing what to do, without any specific goal or direction.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>방랑 [방ː낭]</dt><br>
<dd>wandering; roaming</dd><br>
<dd>목적지 없이 이리저리 떠돌아다님.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of wandering around without a destination.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>